<P>
   BBO-BALLPARK-JOURNEY (Undated) _ Despite living on the East
Coast for almost a decade, I have visited Tiger Stadium at least
once each year, along with other baseball stadiums along the
vacation trail. This summer, because my son is seeking a college,
we journeyed from coast to coast, from campus to campus, and from
ball park to ball park. By Joe Lapointe.
</P>
<P>
   LIPSTYE-COLUMN (Undated) _ A roundup of a recent spate of sports
books. By Robert Lipsyte.
</P>
<P>
   FBO-ARATON-COLUMN (Undated) _ On Friday Night Lights in the
Bronx: traditionally powerful Kennedy H.S. plays its first football
game under the lights on its new field after having its previous
field condemned. By Harvey Araton.
</P>
