<P>
   REPUBS-SPEND (Washington) _ As the new fiscal year approaches, a
financial and political crisis confronts Republicans in Congress.
They may have to break their repeated promises and raid Social
Security to run the government, their own staff and independent
analysts say. By Tim Weiner.
</P>
<P>
   (Story has moved in ``w'' news file.)
