u i BC-AUSTRALIA-ASIA-REVIEW     09-25 0435
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-AUSTRALIA-ASIA-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 SYDNEY, Australia: in mind.  
<TEXT>
