<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-25 15:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5891 &Cx1f; tad-z
u s BC-HKN-PREVIEW-STARS26-C     09-25 0318
