   BUSH-TAXES _ AUSTIN, Tex. _ Although he's been touting
back-to-back tax cuts on the presidential campaign trail, Gov.
George W. Bush's latest $1 billion tax cut seems to have had little
effect as a statewide survey shows that one in three school
districts is either keeping the same tax rate as last year or is
increasing their tax rate. (Elizondo, Austin American-Statesman).
</P>
